ZH: 这个村庄位于山脚下。
EN: This village is situated at the foot of the mountain.

ZH: 我在村庄里度过了童年。
EN: I spent my childhood in the village.

ZH: 那个村庄有很多古老的建筑。
EN: That village has many old buildings.

ZH: 这个村庄的风景非常美丽。
EN: The scenery of this village is very beautiful.

ZH: 这个村庄的居民都非常友好。
EN: The residents of this village are all very friendly.

ZH: 我计划明年去这个村庄旅游。
EN: I plan to visit this village next year.

ZH: 村庄里有一个小溪流经而过。
EN: There is a small stream running through the village.

ZH: 这个村庄的居民主要以农业为生。
EN: The residents of this village mainly make a living through agriculture.

ZH: 这个村庄的生活节奏很慢。
EN: The pace of life in this village is very slow.

ZH: 这个村庄的居民都非常勤劳。
EN: The residents of this village are all very hardworking.

ZH: 他来自一个偏僻的渔村。
EN: He comes from an isolated fishing village.

ZH: 在我们中间的村庄，没有草地。
EN: There is no grassland in our village.

ZH: 这个村庄的居民大多数信奉佛教。
EN: The majority of the residents in this village believe in Buddhism.

ZH: 村庄的孩子们喜欢在河流边玩耍。
EN: The children in the village love to play by the river.

ZH: 那个村庄的房屋都是用木头建造的。
EN: The houses in that village are all made of wood.

ZH: 这个村庄的居民过着简朴的生活。
EN: The residents of this village live a simple life.

ZH: 村子里有一个古老的庙宇。
EN: There is an ancient temple in the village.

ZH: 这个村庄的居民主要以渔业为生。
EN: The residents of this village mainly make a living through fishing.

ZH: 这个村庄的居民都非常热情好客。
EN: The residents of this village are all very hospitable.

ZH: 我喜欢到村庄里度过一个宁静的周末。
EN: I like to spend a peaceful weekend in the village.
